{"tid":2142251,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"OU心理學 定東華醫療科學","createTime":"2020-08-06T09:35:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-06T11:13:21.000Z","uid":308979,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"00aca6841974bc22aebdfd0d87d6c367188a17ac","tid":2142251,"uid":308979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T09:35:31.000Z","msg":"我已經完成左兩年social science asso~ <br />\n黎緊準備繼續讀degree<br />\nOU 個邊其實好早已經offer左applied psychology year 2比我 我一早都諗住求個大學學位咁入去讀多三年畢業就算啦 <br />\n但早兩個星期東華就派左醫療科學學位比我<br />\n我開頭好開心有得讀醫療既 因為好似需求都大 <br />\n但後尾係網上都見到有人話呢科都伏 出黎其實冇咩野可以做 <br />\n求讀緊呢科既人 或者畢業生分享經驗😭 <br />\n因為東華BMS都幾貴 唔想白白用父母太多錢"},{"pid":"76dbde94aaf402a24c2205d8dad11e7d27bc0f85","tid":2142251,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T09:42:13.000Z","msg":"ou同東大都係學店<br />\n所以個問題只係<br />\n心理學vs醫療科學"},{"pid":"42600fad2682dc0696263904bab8de6a5ad01460","tid":2142251,"uid":312363,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T09:42:43.000Z","msg":"一定係ou<br />\n你估醫療就請你咩<br />\n排隊都未論到你啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c00e2fb5c0487702c98b8af1c9d1d9bcef2526c","tid":2142251,"uid":108943,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T09:43:41.000Z","msg":"港大心理都乞食 何況OU"},{"pid":"87134bab6c5982095dddfa08e662effcd546aa06","tid":2142251,"uid":308979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76dbde94aaf402a24c2205d8dad11e7d27bc0f85","tid":2142251,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T09:42:13.000Z","msg":"ou同東大都係學店<br />\n所以個問題只係<br />\n心理學vs醫療科學"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T09:55:58.000Z","msg":"都係～ 我唔知東華醫療出路好唔好 <br />\nTo be honest 如果佢出到黎同我讀心理學一樣廢既 咁點解我要每年比成9萬6蚊落鹹水海<br />\n屋企又唔係有錢 我讀醫療都要借政府先有錢讀到"},{"pid":"f97ee8fcf8095989077153b25989aa6ea4e376ff","tid":2142251,"uid":131262,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"87134bab6c5982095dddfa08e662effcd546aa06","tid":2142251,"uid":308979,"like":0,"